LOUIS F. RAYMOND, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER-RESPONDENT, v. JAMES S. CREGAR, ET AL., DEFENDANTS-RESPONDENTS-PETITIONERS. Mr. George Duggan and Mr. Thomas L. Parsonnet for the plaintiff-petitioner-respondent. Messrs. Biher, Danzig, Marsh & Scherer and Mr. Louis Ogust for the defendants-respondents-petitioners. April 30, 1962.
